{"tid":1655301,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"【私隱問題】Apple回應Safari「送中」問題 只有中國用戶連騰訊","createTime":"2019-10-15T03:56:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-15T10:30:54.000Z","uid":83518,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"d76fa3abeeaa3eeb3238badb227ad55f587cef28","tid":1655301,"uid":83518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T03:56:22.000Z","msg":"Apple近日爆岀Safari私隱問題疑慮，外國有網站發現原來自iOS12.2beta開始，Safari的「詐騙網站警告」功能有可能會把用戶IP資料傳送到騰訊，在這敏感時刻，當然令不少香港人擔心。不過Apple終於正式對此作出回應，某程度上釋除了不少人的疑慮。回應指「Safari會根據已知詐騙網站列表檢查網站URL，並當用戶到訪懷疑是詐騙網站的URL時對用戶顯示警告訊息。在這過程中，Safari會從Google接收了一個已識辨為詐騙網站的列表。區域設定為中國大陸的設備將從騰訊接收詐騙網站列表。」即是只有中國用戶才會在過程中經過騰訊，其他用戶只會經Google。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20191015&amp;s=10829392&amp;a=60155179\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20191015%26s%3D10829392%26a%3D60155179&d=P9V%2Fg5HR%2BYIczjwvlITT9F8MSy0xNzs2bKpftArA8vk%3D&h=c762078a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20191015%26s%3D10829392%26a%3D60155179&h=e30813af\" target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20191015&amp;s=10829392&amp;a=60155179</a>"},{"pid":"bf2e44b82670e8dfe0d8a1edbf07588e3b5af1a3","tid":1655301,"uid":12628,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T04:00:06.000Z","msg":"Safari 送中呢單野講得過去，<br />\n但ios 自我政治審查剔除中華民國國旗呢單奶共野，<br />\n點都講唔過去！"},{"pid":"8b5ea2bbfacb299ffeaa7359034331d9242b8449","tid":1655301,"uid":4503,"like":42,"dislike":1,"score":41,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T04:00:54.000Z","msg":"拿拿拿 <br />\n<br />\n香港同台灣 計中國定非中國先<br />\n<br />\n答又死唔答又死"},{"pid":"d11bd5db00b8a212f9c4bbd40e2c7a65e85b19ea","tid":1655301,"uid":323443,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8b5ea2bbfacb299ffeaa7359034331d9242b8449","tid":1655301,"uid":4503,"like":42,"dislike":1,"score":41,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T04:00:54.000Z","msg":"拿拿拿 <br />\n<br />\n香港同